==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Conglobe
<hw>Con*globe"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To collect, unite, or
coalesce in a round mass.</def> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Conglobulate</ent>⟦br⟧
